01:05:13,702 --> 01:05:16,663
She was like, "Why don't you
come up and open for me?"

1106
01:05:16,830 --> 01:05:20,459
- Get out of here.
- He went up. Swear to God. In England.

1107
01:05:20,626 --> 01:05:23,003
I forgot the theater,
but it was like 5000 people...

1108
01:05:23,170 --> 01:05:26,924
...and he walks out on the stage,
just him and his plug-in acoustic...

1109
01:05:27,091 --> 01:05:30,135
...and he played a Beatles song...

1110
01:05:30,302 --> 01:05:31,345
...which I won't hum.

1111
01:05:32,805 --> 01:05:36,058
M.J., would you do me a favor?
I forgot my drink inside.

1112
01:05:39,812 --> 01:05:43,357
A little Spidey-sense. Something...

1113
01:05:46,819 --> 01:05:48,445
What could go wrong
in Times Square?

1114
01:05:48,612 --> 01:05:49,613
Right.

1115
01:05:49,780 --> 01:05:54,701
- Have you seen my father around?
- Well, I'm not sure if he's coming.

1116
01:05:57,663 --> 01:05:59,832
Oh, I think he's coming.

1117
01:06:06,672 --> 01:06:09,174
- What is that?
- Must be new this year.

1118
01:06:14,054 --> 01:06:15,305
What is that?

1119
01:06:15,472 --> 01:06:16,557
That's our glider!

1120
01:06:26,275 --> 01:06:28,235
One of the times
when Sam is at his best...

1121
01:06:28,402 --> 01:06:31,697
...Sam Raimi, is doing the scenes
with lots of extras...

1122
01:06:31,864 --> 01:06:36,493
...when he comes out
to inspire them...

1123
01:06:37,828 --> 01:06:40,581
...and try to get the reactions
