1133
01:07:29,713 --> 01:07:32,549
I was a big Superman fan as a kid.

1134
01:07:33,675 --> 01:07:36,470
Well, you know, I was that age.

1135
01:07:39,264 --> 01:07:41,058
Very tasteful deaths.

