01:07:49,608 --> 01:07:53,403
That was Laura Ziskin's daughter.
Our producer.

1139
01:07:56,823 --> 01:08:01,870
Willem basically was insisting
on doing almost everything himself.

1140
01:08:02,037 --> 01:08:03,330
Yeah?

1141
01:08:03,789 --> 01:08:05,666
And part of the reason was...

1142
01:08:07,125 --> 01:08:10,420
...because he's so specific with
his physicality of the character.

1143
01:08:10,587 --> 01:08:13,131
And the stuntmen were great, but...

