1145
01:08:18,303 --> 01:08:21,348
He really acts
with every ounce of his body.

1146
01:08:22,391 --> 01:08:25,936
And he's very in shape.
He's a seasoned yogi...

1147
01:08:26,103 --> 01:08:27,980
...and has a lot of control...

1148
01:08:28,939 --> 01:08:30,357
...of his body...

1149
01:08:30,857 --> 01:08:35,237
